{"tid":418341,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"遊日韓注意！HK Express突取消黃金周18航班 逾3,000客受阻","createTime":"2017-09-29T12:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T22:24:04.000Z","uid":41914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ebba055d65167e95104eea4bee114fd81a600f","tid":418341,"uid":41914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"10.1黃金周遊日韓HK Express（香港快運）乘客注意！民航處證實，昨日下午接獲HK Express通知，突然取消18班，由10月1日至8日，往返香港與大阪、名古屋及首爾的定期航班。民航處指，由於正值國慶日和中秋節假期，外遊人數較多，民航處高度關注事件對受影響旅客帶來的不便和影響，已即時聯絡香港快運航空了解事件，並於今早召見了航空公司管理層，要求該航空公司盡快聯絡受影響的旅客作出退款或其他安排。<br />\n<br />\n該公司管理層向民航處稱，已聯絡受影響旅客，並會提供其他航班供受影響旅客轉乘或安排退款。對於有航空公司在外遊高峰期前夕，作出如此大的航班改動，以致影響乘客眾多，當局認為情況極不理想。 至於導致今次航班取消的詳細原因，處方仍在了解中。民航處會要求香港快運航空提交詳細報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57272247&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57272247%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=dY%2BwcgPoOsdsY2SB3VcuJ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9474bd43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57272247%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=eaa91fb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57272247&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"6e8244f811d6533626458244dc35c437851cd1a8","tid":418341,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b89bb2eb476cf20fcdf74d032cc92320848e7e","tid":418341,"uid":41914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d411095c591d0554fc270db9ed70dfd5b288ee","tid":418341,"uid":83709,"like":0,"disl